#: app/templates/landing.html:676
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Mapeo comunitario"

#: app/templates/landing.html:678
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public\n"
"            facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"El Field Tasking Manager permite a las comunidades mapear asentamientos "
"informales, instalaciones públicas y servicios locales para una "
"planificación inclusiva."

#: app/templates/landing.html:683
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Planificación y gestión urbana"

#: app/templates/landing.html:685
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities\n"
"            through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Construya ciudades más inteligentes con encuestas coordinadas de casas, "
"caminos y servicios públicos mediante tareas de mapeo claras y "
"manejables."

#: app/templates/landing.html:690
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Respuesta y recuperación ante desastres"

#: app/templates/landing.html:692
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate "
"volunteers, and\n"
"            deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Mapee rápidamente infraestructura dañada después de desastres, coordine "
"voluntarios y entregue datos confiables para operaciones de socorro."

